'''拉法基湖－道格拉斯站'''（{{lang-en|Lafarge Lake–Douglas Station}}）是[[加拿大|加拿大]][[卑詩省|卑詩省]][[大溫哥華地區|大溫哥華地區]][[高貴林|高貴林]]一座[[溫哥華架空列車|架空列車]][[千禧線|千禧線]]車站。此站位於高貴林市喬德福路（{{lang|en|Guildford Way}}）與松樹路（{{lang|en|Pinetree Way}}）的交界處以北，為[[運輸聯線|運輸聯線]]收費架構中三號收費區的其中一個車站。此站以鄰近的拉法基湖和[[道格拉斯學院|道格拉斯學院]]林思齊校園命名，而高貴林市政廳亦位於此站附近。此站設有150個[[停車換乘|停車換乘]]泊車位，由高貴林市政府管理<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/InformationSheets/160912_EGL_Infosheet_Parking.pdf|title=Parking at Evergreen Stations|publisher=卑詩省政府|accessdate=2016-12-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161202101206/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/InformationSheets/160912_EGL_Infosheet_Parking.pdf|archive-date=2016-12-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

此站在原計劃中稱為道格拉斯學院站（{{lang|en|Douglas College Station}}）<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/Postcards/120817_ELRT_GeneralInfo_Postcard_FINAL.pdf|title=Evergreen Line General Information Postcard|publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Transportation|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130320035608/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/Postcards/120817_ELRT_GeneralInfo_Postcard_FINAL.pdf|archive-date=2013-03-20|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，2013年3月則改為現稱<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/news/20130324/vap1h.htm|title=長青線敲定7站名 造價14.3億 連接本滿高3市|publisher=《明報》加西版|date=2013-03-24|accessdate=2013-03-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130427032659/http://www.mingpaovan.com/htm/news/20130324/vap1h.htm|archivedate=2013-04-27}}</ref>。此站的前期工程和高架路軌工程於2013年夏季展開，車站主體建築則於同年秋季動工<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/CommunityUpdates/130327_CommunityUpdate5.pdf|title=Community Update No. 5 - Looking ahead: Evergreen Line construction activities|page=26|date=2013-06|publisher=British Columbia Ministry of Transportation|accessdate=2013-06-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605160313/http://www.evergreenline.gov.bc.ca/documents/CommunityUpdates/130327_CommunityUpdate5.pdf|archive-date=2013-06-05|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，並於2016年12月2日聯同千禧線的[[長青延線|長青延線]]一起開幕<ref name="open-date">{{cite news|last1=Brown|first1=Scott|title=TransLink will open Evergreen Line on Dec. 2|date=2016-11-07|accessdate=2016-11-07|work=Vancouver Sun|url=http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|archive-date=2016-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161107222150/http://vancouversun.com/news/local-news/translink-will-open-evergreen-line-on-dec-2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|title=Tri-Cities rejoice: The long-awaited Evergreen Line opens|publisher=CTV Vancouver|date=2016-12-02|accessdate=2016-12-02|archive-date=2016-12-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161203153512/http://bc.ctvnews.ca/tri-cities-rejoice-the-long-awaited-evergreen-line-opens-1.3186748|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

